# SalesVault — React Native Expo Mobile App

Build a production-ready, modern minimalist mobile app for the SalesVault stock management system using **Expo 54 + expo-router + TypeScript**.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This plan creates **~50 files** across the mobile app. The existing `mobile-app/` Expo scaffold will be restructured — default boilerplate files will be replaced.

> [!WARNING]
> The backend server must be running on a reachable URL. The app defaults to `http://localhost:3000/api/v1` — you'll need to change this to your machine's IP for physical device testing.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Expo 54, React Native 0.81 |
| Navigation | expo-router v6 (file-based routing) |
| State | Zustand (lightweight, minimal boilerplate) |
| HTTP | Axios (interceptors for JWT refresh) |
| Tokens | expo-secure-store (encrypted storage) |
| Forms | React Hook Form + Zod validation |
| Icons | @expo/vector-icons (Ionicons) |
| Haptics | expo-haptics (micro-interactions) |

---

## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1 — Foundation (Dependencies + Design System + API Layer)

#### [MODIFY] [package.json](file:///c:/Users/mrnad/OneDrive/Desktop/salesvault-stock-management%20system/mobile-app/package.json)
Add: `zustand`, `axios`, `expo-secure-store`, `react-hook-form`, `@hookform/resolvers`, `zod`, `date-fns`

#### [NEW] src/constants/theme.ts
Modern minimalist design tokens: colors (slate palette, accent blue-violet), typography, spacing, border radius, shadows. Dark/light mode support.

#### [NEW] src/constants/api.ts
API base URL + all endpoint paths.

#### [NEW] src/services/api.ts
Axios instance with request/response interceptors:
- Auto-attach JWT `Authorization` header
- Auto-refresh expired tokens via 401 interceptor
- Centralized error handling

#### [NEW] src/services/auth.ts
Token storage/retrieval using expo-secure-store. Login, refresh, logout functions.

#### [NEW] src/stores/auth-store.ts
Zustand auth store: user, tokens, isAuthenticated, login(), logout(), refreshToken().

---

### Phase 2 — Auth Screens

#### [NEW] app/(auth)/login.tsx
Clean login screen: email + password, form validation, loading state, error display, account lock message.

#### [NEW] app/(auth)/_layout.tsx
Auth stack layout (unauthenticated routes).

---

### Phase 3 — App Shell & Navigation

#### [MODIFY] app/_layout.tsx
Root layout: check auth state, redirect to login or app. Splash screen handling.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/_layout.tsx
Main app layout with bottom tab navigation:
- **Dashboard** (home icon)
- **Products** (cube icon)
- **Sales** (cart icon)  
- **Activity** (list icon)
- **Profile** (person icon)

Tab visibility adapts per role (Admin sees all, Salesperson sees relevant tabs).

---

### Phase 4 — Dashboard Screen

#### [NEW] app/(app)/index.tsx (Dashboard)
- **Admin/Manager**: Sales today card, monthly sales card, low stock alerts list, top salespersons, recent system activity feed
- **Salesperson**: My sales today, my stock overview, my recent activity feed
- Pull-to-refresh, skeleton loading states

---

### Phase 5 — CRUD Screens

#### [NEW] app/(app)/products/index.tsx
Product list with search bar, active/inactive filter, paginated FlatList.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/products/[id].tsx
Product detail view.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/products/create.tsx
Create product form (Admin/Manager only).

#### [NEW] app/(app)/warehouses/index.tsx
Warehouse list.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/stock/index.tsx
Stock levels view + low stock alerts.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/stock/assign.tsx
Assign stock to salesperson form (Admin/Manager only).

---

### Phase 6 — Sales Screens

#### [NEW] app/(app)/sales/index.tsx
Sales list with filters (date range, status, salesperson).

#### [NEW] app/(app)/sales/create.tsx
Create sale form: select products from assigned stock, enter quantities, idempotency key auto-generated. Prevents double-tap.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/sales/[id].tsx
Sale detail with line items.

---

### Phase 7 — Activity & Profile Screens

#### [NEW] app/(app)/activity/index.tsx
Activity log feed with filters (by type, user, date range). Hash chain integrity badge.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/profile/index.tsx
User profile, logout button, app version. Admin: user management link.

#### [NEW] app/(app)/users/index.tsx
User list (Admin only).

#### [NEW] app/(app)/users/create.tsx
Create user form (Admin only).

---

### Phase 8 — Shared Components

#### [NEW] src/components/ui/
- `Button.tsx` — Primary/secondary/danger variants with loading spinner
- `Input.tsx` — Styled text input with label, error, icons
- `Card.tsx` — Elevated card with subtle shadow
- `Badge.tsx` — Status badges (PENDING, PAID, CANCELLED)
- `EmptyState.tsx` — Empty list placeholder
- `SkeletonLoader.tsx` — Shimmer loading placeholder
- `StatCard.tsx` — Dashboard metric cards
