## Design System

| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Primary | `#6366F1` (indigo-500) |
| Background | `#FAFAFA` (light) / `#0F172A` (dark) |
| Surface | `#FFFFFF` / `#1E293B` |
| Text | `#0F172A` / `#F8FAFC` |
| Muted | `#94A3B8` |
| Success | `#22C55E` |
| Danger | `#EF4444` |
| Border radius | 12px (cards), 10px (inputs), 24px (buttons) |
| Font | System default (San Francisco / Roboto) |

