## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. `npx expo start` → app loads on Expo Go
2. Login flow works → JWT stored securely
3. Dashboard shows real data from backend
4. Create sale → stock deducted → activity logged
5. Role-based navigation: admin sees all tabs, salesperson sees limited
